nt when the full radial range from\n0 to ~2 virial radii is considered, unless the sample used to determine the\nnumber density profile is restricted to the early-type galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Jan 2003 12:19:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
