erator as only input. From this result we prove that all\npositive and negative equations in the hierarchies share the same sets of local\nand nonlocal constants of the motion for KdV, which are explicitly obtained\nusing the local and nonlocal action principles for KdV.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Jan 2003 18:53:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 11 Jul 2003 22:32:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-26"}
